    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? I\u2019m selling my car and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It\u2019s been well-loved and runs like a dream, making it perfect for your daily commute or those fun weekend getaways. It\u2019s super comfortable, looks great, and is just waiting for a new owner to take the wheel. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
