      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies for razor-sharp response. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M-differential, delivering torque effectively to the tarmac. It features critical preventative maintenance, including a reinforced rear subframe and a serviced VANOS system to ensure timing precision. With a chassis that remains taut and a linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline, this vehicle offers a pure, mechanical connection often lost in modern counterparts.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Reliable performance. Clean title. Regular maintenance performed.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of well-maintained engineering, offering a balance of performance and comfort. The exterior retains its original luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather upholstery is supple with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technological features, including the premium sound system and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having undergone regular synthetic oil changes and a recent full inspection that included new brake rotors and tires. The engine runs smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, seamless shifts. It comes with a complete set of service records and both original keys, making it a reliable choice for a discerning buyer looking for a turn-key experience.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a sophisticated balance of performance and value. Meticulously maintained and presenting in commendable condition, it offers a refined driving experience supported by a history of consistent care. Every major system has been scrutinized to ensure mechanical integrity, making this an exemplary selection for those who demand reliability and professional-grade presentation.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it has been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years\u2014perfect for everything from grocery runs to long weekend road trips! It\u2019s been well-loved, stays clean, and runs like a dream. I\u2019m honestly a bit sad to see it go, but I know it\u2019s going to make the next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW M-division engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response throughout the rev range. The power is managed by a 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring maximum traction during corner exit. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed, mitigating the primary longitudinal stress concerns of this chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec McPherson strut front and multi-link rear geometry, providing the communicative steering feel and balanced weight distribution this era is known for. While the exterior shows minor road-wear consistent with a dedicated driver, the mechanical synchronization and drivetrain rigidity remain tight and responsive.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
